[
  {
    "text": "The number one question we get\nasked is, how many tries does",
    "start": 0.0,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "it take to make a trick shot?",
    "start": 2.46,
    "duration": 1.208
  },
  {
    "text": "The number two question--\nhow are you guys so ripped?",
    "start": 3.668,
    "duration": 3.174
  },
  {
    "text": "[SCREAMS] Welcome to\n\"World's Strongest Dude.\"",
    "start": 6.842,
    "duration": 3.743
  },
  {
    "text": "[CLUB DANGER, \"LIVING LEGEND\"]\nI'm a living legend.",
    "start": 10.585,
    "duration": 2.125
  },
  {
    "text": "Today we have set up four\nrigorous physical challenges",
    "start": 12.71,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "to determine once and for all\nwho is the strongest dude.",
    "start": 15.23,
    "duration": 3.938
  },
  {
    "text": "[YELLING]",
    "start": 19.168,
    "duration": 1.272
  },
  {
    "text": "People say this doesn't\nhappen overnight.",
    "start": 20.44,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "And they're 100% right.",
    "start": 22.22,
    "duration": 0.965
  },
  {
    "text": "But with two-day\nshipping, it can",
    "start": 23.185,
    "duration": 1.375
  },
  {
    "text": "happen in two nights, which\nis kind of what we did.",
    "start": 24.56,
    "duration": 2.85
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to the\n2023 Swole Battle.",
    "start": 27.41,
    "duration": 2.73
  },
  {
    "text": "First up on the\ncompetition, bag throw--",
    "start": 30.14,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "60-pounds bags, 11-foot hurdle.",
    "start": 32.57,
    "duration": 2.337
  },
  {
    "text": "You clear it, you move on.",
    "start": 34.907,
    "duration": 1.083
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't, you're out.",
    "start": 35.99,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, boys.",
    "start": 36.89,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "You have 20 seconds.",
    "start": 37.557,
    "duration": 0.923
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody Jones.",
    "start": 38.48,
    "duration": 1.61
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 40.09,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That'll work.",
    "start": 40.59,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Boom!",
    "start": 41.39,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Been working hard,\nso very excited.",
    "start": 42.17,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "Go for it, Garrett.",
    "start": 44.18,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Easy breezy.",
    "start": 45.29,
    "duration": 0.94
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 46.23,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty.",
    "start": 46.73,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "He went for the one\nhand, pun intended.",
    "start": 47.27,
    "duration": 1.545
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 48.815,
    "duration": 0.255
  },
  {
    "text": "That will work.",
    "start": 49.07,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "[SLAPPING]",
    "start": 49.88,
    "duration": 1.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah-choo.",
    "start": 51.87,
    "duration": 1.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Sup, guys.",
    "start": 53.78,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Cor-- sorry, hold\non just a second.",
    "start": 54.28,
    "duration": 1.822
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah.",
    "start": 56.102,
    "duration": 0.982
  },
  {
    "text": "Pff, pff, pff.",
    "start": 57.084,
    "duration": 2.046
  },
  {
    "text": "Get up!",
    "start": 59.13,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[RECORD SCRATCH]",
    "start": 59.63,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh a wedgie.",
    "start": 60.39,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 61.75,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No way!",
    "start": 62.25,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "The timer's counting.",
    "start": 63.15,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "The timer's counting.",
    "start": 64.05,
    "duration": 0.989
  },
  {
    "text": "Timer's counting.",
    "start": 65.039,
    "duration": 1.531
  },
  {
    "text": "A nightmare situation\nfor the swole boy.",
    "start": 66.57,
    "duration": 2.73
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to help you out.",
    "start": 69.3,
    "duration": 2.244
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, it didn't go over.",
    "start": 71.544,
    "duration": 0.996
  },
  {
    "text": "5 seconds left.",
    "start": 72.54,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Corey has to have this throw.",
    "start": 73.56,
    "duration": 2.605
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 76.165,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, yeah.",
    "start": 76.665,
    "duration": 0.435
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 77.1,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's done it.",
    "start": 77.6,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "It took all the juice.",
    "start": 78.48,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, baby.",
    "start": 80.56,
    "duration": 0.86
  },
  {
    "text": "I have a pretty\ndevastating shoulder injury",
    "start": 81.42,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "from a recent fight scene.",
    "start": 83.43,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Really let myself go.",
    "start": 84.6,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "One arm is all I need.",
    "start": 85.8,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "We're out of\ncommission over here.",
    "start": 86.85,
    "duration": 1.417
  },
  {
    "text": "Who cares, baby?",
    "start": 88.267,
    "duration": 0.923
  },
  {
    "text": "Get a little swing into it.",
    "start": 89.19,
    "duration": 2.148
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my goodness.",
    "start": 91.338,
    "duration": 1.422
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa!",
    "start": 92.76,
    "duration": 0.948
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 93.708,
    "duration": 1.422
  },
  {
    "text": "That was wild.",
    "start": 95.13,
    "duration": 2.73
  },
  {
    "text": "Some of my most\nsuccessful performances",
    "start": 97.86,
    "duration": 1.95
  },
  {
    "text": "have been kind of in\nthe chubby-dubby world.",
    "start": 99.81,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "The, Chubby!",
    "start": 101.85,
    "duration": 1.246
  },
  {
    "text": "Dubby!",
    "start": 103.096,
    "duration": 1.274
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 104.37,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "My strengths are\nobviously my biceps.",
    "start": 104.87,
    "duration": 3.15
  },
  {
    "text": "I know you're talking\nabout personality stuff.",
    "start": 108.02,
    "duration": 2.49
  },
  {
    "text": "Good friend and kind\nof funny sometimes.",
    "start": 110.51,
    "duration": 3.09
  },
  {
    "text": "And also my pecs.",
    "start": 113.6,
    "duration": 1.515
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS]",
    "start": 115.115,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "Coby-- I think he's been\nfocusing on lifting his fork.",
    "start": 116.99,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sorry.",
    "start": 120.02,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "I know I shouldn't\ntalk with my mouth full",
    "start": 120.56,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Fork, mouth, fork, mouth.",
    "start": 121.7,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "He's got that part\nto figured out.",
    "start": 122.742,
    "duration": 1.416
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a big sandwich.",
    "start": 124.158,
    "duration": 0.932
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS]",
    "start": 125.09,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone's through\nthe 11-foot hurdle.",
    "start": 125.72,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "On to 12.",
    "start": 127.46,
    "duration": 0.719
  },
  {
    "text": "That'll work.",
    "start": 130.96,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 131.59,
    "duration": 0.811
  },
  {
    "text": "Ha.",
    "start": 132.401,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS RAPIDLY]",
    "start": 132.901,
    "duration": 1.749
  },
  {
    "text": "What a dumb question.",
    "start": 134.65,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "What are your strengths?",
    "start": 135.82,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know.",
    "start": 137.06,
    "duration": 0.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you not tell?",
    "start": 137.65,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, look at me.",
    "start": 139.24,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Cory barely clears 11 feet.",
    "start": 140.41,
    "duration": 1.485
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see if he can get 12.",
    "start": 141.895,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "[BUZZER]",
    "start": 143.02,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's now or never time.",
    "start": 143.52,
    "duration": 2.87
  },
  {
    "text": "[BUZZER]",
    "start": 146.39,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That's about all\nthe juice he has.",
    "start": 146.89,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "Cobes, let's get it, baby.",
    "start": 148.36,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel like I more or\nless have it in the bag.",
    "start": 149.65,
    "duration": 1.917
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.",
    "start": 151.567,
    "duration": 1.123
  },
  {
    "text": "The spin cycle",
    "start": 152.69,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "[SCREAMS]",
    "start": 153.66,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 154.16,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 154.66,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "More or less.",
    "start": 155.63,
    "duration": 0.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on!",
    "start": 156.32,
    "duration": 1.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Man.",
    "start": 158.23,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on!",
    "start": 158.73,
    "duration": 1.652
  },
  {
    "text": "Cory, you've been eliminated.",
    "start": 160.382,
    "duration": 1.208
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Watch me\nmove, turn me loose.",
    "start": 161.59,
    "duration": 4.73
  },
  {
    "text": "[TEST TONE]",
    "start": 166.32,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "On to round two.",
    "start": 166.82,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 167.93,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Out here in the elements filming\nSwole Battle for you guys,",
    "start": 170.39,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "quick merch shoutout.",
    "start": 173.21,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Brand new merch just\ndropped-- new little hoodie.",
    "start": 174.41,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Stop looking at the bod.",
    "start": 176.71,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Just look at the merch.",
    "start": 177.71,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "It looks good in all\nbody types, baby.",
    "start": 178.7,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "Round two-- stone carry.",
    "start": 181.1,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "150-pound boulder,\nleast distance traveled",
    "start": 182.75,
    "duration": 2.85
  },
  {
    "text": "is eliminated.",
    "start": 185.6,
    "duration": 1.008
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, wait a minute.",
    "start": 186.608,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you doing here, boy?",
    "start": 187.4,
    "duration": 0.93
  },
  {
    "text": "[RECORD SCRATCH]",
    "start": 188.33,
    "duration": 0.39
  },
  {
    "text": "You look deflated.",
    "start": 188.72,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel deflated.",
    "start": 189.5,
    "duration": 0.915
  },
  {
    "text": "What happened to your arms?",
    "start": 190.415,
    "duration": 1.125
  },
  {
    "text": "They're gone.",
    "start": 191.54,
    "duration": 0.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, Hilbert.",
    "start": 192.45,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "Good legs.",
    "start": 194.1,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS]",
    "start": 194.6,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh.",
    "start": 195.8,
    "duration": 1.478
  },
  {
    "text": "And he's off.",
    "start": 197.278,
    "duration": 0.542
  },
  {
    "text": "He has got this.",
    "start": 197.82,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 199.11,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "So I work out for one\nthing and one thing only.",
    "start": 199.61,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's to hit\nbombs down fairways.",
    "start": 201.62,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "And this is where misery\nsets in, at about midfield.",
    "start": 203.75,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 206.18,
    "duration": 0.09
  },
  {
    "text": "And to be clear, the\nonly thing I need to lift",
    "start": 206.27,
    "duration": 1.62
  },
  {
    "text": "is that white little ball\nthat sits on the tee.",
    "start": 207.89,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you dare take a\nbreak, Garrett Hilbert.",
    "start": 209.81,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "You keep going, young man.",
    "start": 211.685,
    "duration": 3.255
  },
  {
    "text": "5, 4, 3, 2, 1--",
    "start": 214.94,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "100.",
    "start": 217.7,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "And a second wind.",
    "start": 219.14,
    "duration": 0.93
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go.",
    "start": 220.07,
    "duration": 0.858
  },
  {
    "text": "Coming back.",
    "start": 220.928,
    "duration": 0.936
  },
  {
    "text": "[SHOUTING]",
    "start": 221.864,
    "duration": 1.872
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, I did not see that coming.",
    "start": 223.736,
    "duration": 4.034
  },
  {
    "text": "Joints give out,\nligaments give out.",
    "start": 227.77,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "I missed about eight weeks for\ninjury, tore the right pec--",
    "start": 229.66,
    "duration": 3.69
  },
  {
    "text": "right pec.",
    "start": 233.35,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry.",
    "start": 234.77,
    "duration": 0.62
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS]",
    "start": 235.39,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "121 yards.",
    "start": 236.05,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Good luck beating that, boys.",
    "start": 238.21,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "Congratulations,\nGarrett, 121 yards.",
    "start": 239.62,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Not necessary.",
    "start": 241.69,
    "duration": 0.81
  },
  {
    "text": "I apologize.",
    "start": 242.5,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty, you're up next.",
    "start": 243.1,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Let the big dog eat.",
    "start": 244.48,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Up.",
    "start": 247.116,
    "duration": 0.771
  },
  {
    "text": "Ooh, good technique.",
    "start": 247.887,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, he goes really low.",
    "start": 248.72,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "And he's off.",
    "start": 249.95,
    "duration": 0.83
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 250.78,
    "duration": 1.15
  },
  {
    "text": "People are asking me how I was\nable to carry the rock so well.",
    "start": 251.93,
    "duration": 2.61
  },
  {
    "text": "It was just a daily\nroutine for me, you know.",
    "start": 254.54,
    "duration": 2.19
  },
  {
    "text": "When I was only 12 years\nold, my dad accidentally",
    "start": 256.73,
    "duration": 3.39
  },
  {
    "text": "built our house in a floodplain\nand I had to move it by myself.",
    "start": 260.12,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Physically, I moved the\nhouse out of the floodplain.",
    "start": 262.94,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "And that was a lot\nheavier than the rock.",
    "start": 265.16,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "200.",
    "start": 267.23,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We're going 300, boys.",
    "start": 267.73,
    "duration": 0.917
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, my.",
    "start": 268.647,
    "duration": 0.893
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, very well done.",
    "start": 269.54,
    "duration": 1.992
  },
  {
    "text": "Codes, you're up.",
    "start": 271.532,
    "duration": 0.708
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody Jones.",
    "start": 272.24,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "You've got to beat 121 yards.",
    "start": 272.87,
    "duration": 1.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Go.",
    "start": 274.38,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "I wouldn't sit there too long.",
    "start": 274.88,
    "duration": 1.39
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the epitome\nof a Pelotoner.",
    "start": 276.27,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 278.41,
    "duration": 2.42
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS]",
    "start": 282.282,
    "duration": 2.408
  },
  {
    "text": "And he's off.",
    "start": 284.978,
    "duration": 0.542
  },
  {
    "text": "Just go.",
    "start": 285.52,
    "duration": 1.122
  },
  {
    "text": "Not only do I think\nI'm going to make it,",
    "start": 286.642,
    "duration": 1.708
  },
  {
    "text": "I know I'm going to make it.",
    "start": 288.35,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go!",
    "start": 289.517,
    "duration": 0.723
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry.",
    "start": 290.24,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the preworkout and the\nsupplements and the protein",
    "start": 290.74,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "and then hydrate\nand all the things.",
    "start": 293.71,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS]",
    "start": 295.21,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm the\nbest that's ever been.",
    "start": 297.03,
    "duration": 3.241
  },
  {
    "text": "1 yard away.",
    "start": 300.271,
    "duration": 1.619
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 301.89,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 303.14,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "And he passes Garrett by a yard.",
    "start": 303.64,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "122.",
    "start": 305.54,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "No need to overexert here.",
    "start": 307.34,
    "duration": 2.11
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS]",
    "start": 309.45,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[TEST TONE] Miracles\nstill happen.",
    "start": 309.95,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "We've been there before.",
    "start": 311.71,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "You look hilarious.",
    "start": 312.71,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Why are you still here?",
    "start": 313.82,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh?",
    "start": 315.05,
    "duration": 0.21
  },
  {
    "text": "No?",
    "start": 315.26,
    "duration": 0.45
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it's just--",
    "start": 315.71,
    "duration": 0.15
  },
  {
    "text": "You got eliminated!",
    "start": 315.86,
    "duration": 0.47
  },
  {
    "text": "It's funny to watch, OK?",
    "start": 316.33,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Go home!",
    "start": 317.33,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm on fire.",
    "start": 317.83,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm hot to the touch.",
    "start": 318.86,
    "duration": 1.83
  },
  {
    "text": "The person not to be\nlooking out for is Coby.",
    "start": 320.69,
    "duration": 2.49
  },
  {
    "text": "Haven't seen that kid\nin the gym in years.",
    "start": 323.18,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "He's officially off.",
    "start": 325.16,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Belly meets boulder.",
    "start": 326.39,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go Coby.",
    "start": 327.86,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at the belly\nhanging out from below.",
    "start": 329.63,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, this isn't good.",
    "start": 331.64,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no, it's over.",
    "start": 333.11,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "No.",
    "start": 334.53,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, it's--",
    "start": 335.03,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't give up!",
    "start": 335.53,
    "duration": 1.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Coby, I really can't do\nanything, but I'm here.",
    "start": 336.59,
    "duration": 2.215
  },
  {
    "text": "Just know I'm here for spirit.",
    "start": 338.805,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go!",
    "start": 340.055,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "A stop and go.",
    "start": 341.69,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "A stop and go at midfield.",
    "start": 342.98,
    "duration": 1.578
  },
  {
    "text": "He doesn't have it.",
    "start": 344.558,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, congrats, boys.",
    "start": 345.35,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Hold on.",
    "start": 346.35,
    "duration": 0.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Hold on.",
    "start": 347.26,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, Coby.",
    "start": 348.24,
    "duration": 0.996
  },
  {
    "text": "You're almost there!",
    "start": 349.236,
    "duration": 2.334
  },
  {
    "text": "He pressed the Pause button.",
    "start": 351.57,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Controller disconnected.",
    "start": 353.1,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He's got new batteries in,\nand he's rolling again.",
    "start": 354.6,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Straight for the\ngoal line, Cobes.",
    "start": 356.73,
    "duration": 0.48
  },
  {
    "text": "No way.",
    "start": 357.21,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "You drop that stone!",
    "start": 358.08,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "I would argue the\nstrongman competition",
    "start": 359.34,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "is a lot more about what's\nin here than what's in here.",
    "start": 361.5,
    "duration": 2.565
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, you drop that stone!",
    "start": 366.57,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes!",
    "start": 368.34,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Go!",
    "start": 369.52,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Go, Coby!",
    "start": 370.75,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "You have 15 more yards.",
    "start": 372.19,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERING]",
    "start": 374.11,
    "duration": 2.75
  },
  {
    "text": "121-- now 5 yards.",
    "start": 376.86,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "No, you drop it now!",
    "start": 378.98,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Passed 121.",
    "start": 381.11,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "He has done it.",
    "start": 382.58,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "He's done it!",
    "start": 383.45,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "And now he's just showing off.",
    "start": 384.15,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 385.85,
    "duration": 0.94
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 386.79,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Coby!",
    "start": 387.29,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "[SHOUTING]",
    "start": 389.69,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Chubby Coby is an\nabsolute certified problem",
    "start": 394.01,
    "duration": 2.717
  },
  {
    "text": "at this point.",
    "start": 396.727,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Was I shocked that Coby made it?",
    "start": 397.31,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Absolutely.",
    "start": 398.84,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd say that's the biggest\nsurprise of the day.",
    "start": 399.44,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Second biggest shock of the day\nwas the lady coming up to me",
    "start": 401.18,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "in the grocery store while\nI was shopping for oranges",
    "start": 403.31,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "and asked me if I\nwas Mr. Incredible.",
    "start": 405.29,
    "duration": 1.542
  },
  {
    "text": "Was I wearing a red spandex\nshirt that was too small?",
    "start": 406.832,
    "duration": 2.328
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes.",
    "start": 409.16,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But it was still\nshocking at the time,",
    "start": 409.67,
    "duration": 1.643
  },
  {
    "text": "just because I'm\nnot used to this.",
    "start": 411.313,
    "duration": 1.417
  },
  {
    "text": "Garrett has been\neliminated, only 121 yards.",
    "start": 412.73,
    "duration": 2.55
  },
  {
    "text": "So Ty, Cody, and Coby will\nbe headed to round three.",
    "start": 415.28,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 418.34,
    "duration": 1.719
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm on fire.",
    "start": 422.957,
    "duration": 0.966
  },
  {
    "text": "Onto Hercules hold, round three,\nand there's only three left--",
    "start": 423.923,
    "duration": 3.517
  },
  {
    "text": "Chubb Cobes, Cody, Ty.",
    "start": 427.44,
    "duration": 1.905
  },
  {
    "text": "And if you want to hold\na spot in the finale,",
    "start": 429.345,
    "duration": 1.875
  },
  {
    "text": "you'd better hold\non for dear life.",
    "start": 431.22,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "You're going to hold these\npillars for as long as you can.",
    "start": 432.54,
    "duration": 2.417
  },
  {
    "text": "Whatever time is the\nlowest, that person's out.",
    "start": 434.957,
    "duration": 2.111
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, Ty, you're first up.",
    "start": 437.068,
    "duration": 1.292
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's get started.",
    "start": 438.36,
    "duration": 0.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you, sport.",
    "start": 439.12,
    "duration": 1.977
  },
  {
    "text": "One thing that I like to do\njust to get mentally focused",
    "start": 441.097,
    "duration": 2.333
  },
  {
    "text": "and jazzed up for a\ncompetition-- good old",
    "start": 443.43,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "fashioned purple nurples.",
    "start": 445.41,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "[SCREAMS]",
    "start": 446.82,
    "duration": 2.3
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 449.12,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "[HORN BLOWS]",
    "start": 450.5,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And we're underway.",
    "start": 451.88,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler is--",
    "start": 453.4,
    "duration": 0.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Solid start.",
    "start": 454.11,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 454.61,
    "duration": 2.7
  },
  {
    "text": "If I know one thing about\nTy, he's here to win.",
    "start": 457.31,
    "duration": 3.106
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Watch me\nmove, turn me loose.",
    "start": 460.416,
    "duration": 3.192
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me do--",
    "start": 463.608,
    "duration": 0.717
  },
  {
    "text": "There's some grimace.",
    "start": 464.325,
    "duration": 0.875
  },
  {
    "text": "There's some real\ngrimace on the face.",
    "start": 465.2,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "A finale birth on the line.",
    "start": 466.94,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't think he's cold.",
    "start": 472.16,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "I think his arms are tired.",
    "start": 473.33,
    "duration": 1.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 474.96,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the time?",
    "start": 475.46,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "41.5.7.",
    "start": 476.33,
    "duration": 2.997
  },
  {
    "text": "Powdered donuts for lunch.",
    "start": 479.327,
    "duration": 1.083
  },
  {
    "text": "That's the key to victory.",
    "start": 480.41,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "That was impressive.",
    "start": 481.52,
    "duration": 0.93
  },
  {
    "text": "You haven't won a\nbattle in a while.",
    "start": 482.45,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Is this the longest\ndrought of your career?",
    "start": 484.01,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Deep sea, you were close,\nbut that was your fault.",
    "start": 485.97,
    "duration": 2.083
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS]",
    "start": 488.053,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "Last one.",
    "start": 489.02,
    "duration": 0.637
  },
  {
    "text": "You've got one more.",
    "start": 489.657,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Was that on me?",
    "start": 490.49,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "I think so, personally.",
    "start": 491.63,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "OK.",
    "start": 492.86,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "You could have caught more fish.",
    "start": 493.36,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Going up against Cody-- kind of\nanother big shock to the day.",
    "start": 495.02,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "He kind of looks like\na Wii Sports character.",
    "start": 497.78,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm trying to take him\nserious, but it's hard.",
    "start": 499.13,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait, who said that?",
    "start": 500.78,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait, what?",
    "start": 501.74,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty, was it you?",
    "start": 502.34,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Easy, easy.",
    "start": 503.21,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "Easy.",
    "start": 504.56,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I was\nmade, made to win.",
    "start": 506.24,
    "duration": 2.75
  },
  {
    "text": "Look out, I'm going in.",
    "start": 508.99,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler's time's in the can, and\nnow Cody Jones is underway.",
    "start": 511.21,
    "duration": 3.099
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, he wants to\nbe in the finale.",
    "start": 514.309,
    "duration": 1.578
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at this guy.",
    "start": 515.887,
    "duration": 0.708
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 516.595,
    "duration": 3.165
  },
  {
    "text": "I think he's finding\na good mental place.",
    "start": 519.76,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "The Hercules hold is\ndefinitely kind of my nemesis.",
    "start": 522.73,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "Hold it.",
    "start": 525.16,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Physical fortitude\nby Cody Jones.",
    "start": 526.45,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Now he's shaking.",
    "start": 528.97,
    "duration": 1.11
  },
  {
    "text": "I want it!",
    "start": 530.08,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, he's letting to be known.",
    "start": 531.07,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "He's barking.",
    "start": 532.42,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "The dog's barking.",
    "start": 533.14,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "I know I'm big!",
    "start": 534.28,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Legs are shaking,\narms are shaking,",
    "start": 535.51,
    "duration": 1.95
  },
  {
    "text": "brain's not working\nbut Jones still going.",
    "start": 537.46,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on!",
    "start": 540.1,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Let me do what I do.",
    "start": 540.82,
    "duration": 1.67
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 542.49,
    "duration": 1.248
  },
  {
    "text": "Give me 2 more seconds, Cody!",
    "start": 546.372,
    "duration": 1.318
  },
  {
    "text": "[SHOUTS]",
    "start": 547.69,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 549.67,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "What a performance.",
    "start": 550.18,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 550.972,
    "duration": 0.648
  },
  {
    "text": "He can't even put on\nhis glasses, brother.",
    "start": 551.62,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "The tall man with a tall\nperformance-- well done, Jones.",
    "start": 554.14,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "52 seconds.",
    "start": 557.5,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 558.53,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow.",
    "start": 559.03,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Yep.",
    "start": 559.33,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "That means you are safe\nand through to the finale.",
    "start": 559.83,
    "duration": 2.56
  },
  {
    "text": "It all comes down to Coby.",
    "start": 562.39,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Can he bounce Ty?",
    "start": 563.59,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "[RECORD SCRATCH]",
    "start": 564.88,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we do this?",
    "start": 565.93,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, at this\npoint, can we do this?",
    "start": 567.22,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know.",
    "start": 568.91,
    "duration": 0.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Obviously, this is\ngoing to be tough.",
    "start": 569.14,
    "duration": 1.542
  },
  {
    "text": "My strategy is to keep\nit in a little tighter.",
    "start": 570.682,
    "duration": 2.038
  },
  {
    "text": "I believe.",
    "start": 572.72,
    "duration": 0.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you guys believe?",
    "start": 573.25,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "[CRICKETS CHIRPING]",
    "start": 574.12,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't?",
    "start": 575.59,
    "duration": 0.63
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Yeah, yeah.",
    "start": 576.22,
    "duration": 1.45
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 577.67,
    "duration": 0.915
  },
  {
    "text": "That's what I needed.",
    "start": 578.585,
    "duration": 0.875
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I was\nmade, made to win.",
    "start": 579.46,
    "duration": 4.834
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm the best that's ever been.",
    "start": 584.294,
    "duration": 2.706
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 587.0,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "[HORN BLOWS]",
    "start": 587.87,
    "duration": 0.95
  },
  {
    "text": "The chubb is on the way.",
    "start": 588.82,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "He's fighting.",
    "start": 590.15,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 590.75,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Anything's possible!",
    "start": 591.25,
    "duration": 1.742
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on!",
    "start": 592.992,
    "duration": 1.208
  },
  {
    "text": "Will the shoulder hold up?",
    "start": 594.2,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "That's the grand question.",
    "start": 595.55,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I find that a lot of the\npower comes from lower down.",
    "start": 596.93,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Watch me\nmove, turn me loose.",
    "start": 599.81,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me do--",
    "start": 602.17,
    "duration": 0.916
  },
  {
    "text": "Go!",
    "start": 603.086,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend!",
    "start": 603.586,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 605.446,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, the belief was\nas big as his belly.",
    "start": 605.946,
    "duration": 2.884
  },
  {
    "text": "What a run, Coby.",
    "start": 608.83,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "The mystique of the\nchubby-dubby has come to an end.",
    "start": 610.69,
    "duration": 2.49
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 613.18,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Finale, bro!",
    "start": 613.68,
    "duration": 1.803
  },
  {
    "text": "I appreciate it.",
    "start": 615.483,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Good job.",
    "start": 616.15,
    "duration": 0.52
  },
  {
    "text": "I appreciate it.",
    "start": 616.67,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Hats off to Cobes.",
    "start": 617.337,
    "duration": 1.003
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to miss seeing that\nbig old belly out there just",
    "start": 618.34,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "jiggling.",
    "start": 620.35,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Congrats.",
    "start": 620.65,
    "duration": 0.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, congrats on\nmaking the finale.",
    "start": 620.95,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, come on.",
    "start": 622.24,
    "duration": 0.85
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey.",
    "start": 623.09,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoa, hey.",
    "start": 623.59,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 624.1,
    "duration": 0.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey!",
    "start": 624.77,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) 'Cause\nI like the pain.",
    "start": 625.27,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm on--",
    "start": 626.56,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Is this the finale?",
    "start": 627.06,
    "duration": 0.95
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I don't think so.",
    "start": 628.01,
    "duration": 0.875
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS]",
    "start": 628.885,
    "duration": 0.465
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, OK.",
    "start": 629.35,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll find out tomorrow.",
    "start": 629.85,
    "duration": 1.174
  },
  {
    "text": "[SHOUTS]",
    "start": 631.024,
    "duration": 1.776
  },
  {
    "text": "Bicep.",
    "start": 632.8,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Tricep.",
    "start": 633.79,
    "duration": 1.525
  },
  {
    "text": "Gluteus!",
    "start": 635.315,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) I'm a living legend.",
    "start": 635.815,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Finale time in Frisco.",
    "start": 641.03,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty Toney, Cody Jones battling\nout for the Swole Battle",
    "start": 642.2,
    "duration": 2.73
  },
  {
    "text": "Championship.",
    "start": 644.93,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "It's going to start off with\nthe toilet bowl run, 15 yards.",
    "start": 645.65,
    "duration": 2.7
  },
  {
    "text": "They'll drop the porta-potties,\nhead to the Atlas stones, 80-,",
    "start": 648.35,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "100-, 120-pound balls.",
    "start": 651.29,
    "duration": 1.743
  },
  {
    "text": "And then we'll\nhead to the finale,",
    "start": 653.033,
    "duration": 1.417
  },
  {
    "text": "which is the F-150 tug of war.",
    "start": 654.45,
    "duration": 1.85
  },
  {
    "text": "And the winner will plant their\nflag on the Swole Mountain",
    "start": 656.3,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "as the Golden Champion.",
    "start": 658.73,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty, obviously a big\nfavorite tonight.",
    "start": 659.93,
    "duration": 1.943
  },
  {
    "text": "You let that play\ninto your head--",
    "start": 661.873,
    "duration": 1.417
  },
  {
    "text": "[SNORTS]",
    "start": 663.29,
    "duration": 1.228
  },
  {
    "text": "[COUGHS]",
    "start": 664.518,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[TEST TONE]",
    "start": 665.018,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I try and not\nlet that get to me.",
    "start": 665.518,
    "duration": 1.92
  },
  {
    "text": "I try not to listen to\nthe haters, the naysayers,",
    "start": 667.438,
    "duration": 2.042
  },
  {
    "text": "the positive thinkers,\nreally anybody.",
    "start": 669.48,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "I just try and go out\nthere and do my own thing,",
    "start": 671.0,
    "duration": 1.45
  },
  {
    "text": "and-- also, just\na word of advice--",
    "start": 672.45,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "don't chalk up too much\nbefore you do one of these.",
    "start": 673.76,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Your finale moment's\nabout to happen.",
    "start": 675.56,
    "duration": 1.542
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody Jones-- kind of a\ninverse David versus Goliath",
    "start": 677.102,
    "duration": 2.868
  },
  {
    "text": "because it's the taller man\nwho has the very little odds.",
    "start": 679.97,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "You think?",
    "start": 682.41,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "But do you feel like\nyou could possibly",
    "start": 682.91,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "cook up an upset today?",
    "start": 684.92,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 686.45,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "The suit isn't,\nlike, the best look,",
    "start": 687.2,
    "duration": 2.94
  },
  {
    "text": "but I feel like it's\nmore about what's inside",
    "start": 690.14,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "the suit than the actual suit.",
    "start": 692.6,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "If you perform anything like\nyour muffin biceps here,",
    "start": 694.13,
    "duration": 2.262
  },
  {
    "text": "we're in trouble.",
    "start": 696.392,
    "duration": 0.708
  },
  {
    "text": "So good luck to you.",
    "start": 697.1,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 697.94,
    "duration": 0.09
  },
  {
    "text": "You're going to need it.",
    "start": 698.03,
    "duration": 1.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I need it.",
    "start": 699.03,
    "duration": 0.77
  },
  {
    "text": "It's toilet time in Texas.",
    "start": 699.8,
    "duration": 1.62
  },
  {
    "text": "The Swole Battle finale\nstarts in 3, 2, 1.",
    "start": 701.42,
    "duration": 4.62
  },
  {
    "text": "And they're off.",
    "start": 706.04,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[HORN BLOWS]",
    "start": 706.76,
    "duration": 0.926
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, baby.",
    "start": 709.54,
    "duration": 0.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Toilet.",
    "start": 710.26,
    "duration": 0.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Ty--",
    "start": 710.9,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "[SHATTERING]",
    "start": 711.4,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow!",
    "start": 712.32,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 715.08,
    "duration": 0.92
  },
  {
    "text": "We're equal on the Atlas balls.",
    "start": 716.0,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Mano y mano.",
    "start": 718.1,
    "duration": 0.945
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Watch me move, turn\nme loose, let me do what I do.",
    "start": 719.045,
    "duration": 3.855
  },
  {
    "text": "Very even.",
    "start": 722.9,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler done with Atlas stones.",
    "start": 724.23,
    "duration": 1.43
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody now done with Atlas stones.",
    "start": 725.66,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "It's down to a truck tug of war.",
    "start": 727.55,
    "duration": 2.7
  },
  {
    "text": "They both get to the\nF-150 simultaneously.",
    "start": 730.25,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "The F-150 pretty\nstationary early on.",
    "start": 733.28,
    "duration": 3.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Y'all are going to be toast.",
    "start": 736.58,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS]",
    "start": 737.96,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Jones re-evaluating whether\nhe wanted to be in this finale",
    "start": 738.56,
    "duration": 3.18
  },
  {
    "text": "or not.",
    "start": 741.74,
    "duration": 0.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, whoa.",
    "start": 742.52,
    "duration": 0.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, now Jones with\na ferocious pull.",
    "start": 743.04,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Good leverage play\nby the 6'6\" Jones.",
    "start": 745.1,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler, the seasoned veteran,\ncatching his breath.",
    "start": 747.62,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Now with the one-arm technique.",
    "start": 750.5,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "He's going to wrap around.",
    "start": 751.88,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Nice, TT.",
    "start": 752.75,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I like that.",
    "start": 753.35,
    "duration": 0.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Smart.",
    "start": 753.68,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "And now a big pull.",
    "start": 754.18,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, and that one's healthy.",
    "start": 755.06,
    "duration": 1.128
  },
  {
    "text": "Get him back, Cody.",
    "start": 756.188,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "A healthy amount of pull.",
    "start": 756.98,
    "duration": 1.042
  },
  {
    "text": "Now Tyler's got momentum.",
    "start": 758.022,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Now Tyler is tugging.",
    "start": 759.29,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "Jones on life support.",
    "start": 760.94,
    "duration": 1.95
  },
  {
    "text": "(SINGING) Watch me move.",
    "start": 762.89,
    "duration": 1.276
  },
  {
    "text": "[SCREAMING]",
    "start": 764.166,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "And now Jones!",
    "start": 764.666,
    "duration": 3.374
  },
  {
    "text": "The tall man with\nthe tall effort!",
    "start": 768.04,
    "duration": 2.316
  },
  {
    "text": "Wow!",
    "start": 770.356,
    "duration": 1.314
  },
  {
    "text": "This is why you play the game!",
    "start": 771.67,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "This is crazy!",
    "start": 773.92,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Plowing through it.",
    "start": 774.82,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "[GRUNTS] My hands are bleeding.",
    "start": 777.94,
    "duration": 1.91
  },
  {
    "text": "Now CoJo.",
    "start": 779.85,
    "duration": 0.83
  },
  {
    "text": "Can't fault here, Cody.",
    "start": 780.68,
    "duration": 1.41
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 782.09,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no.",
    "start": 783.35,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "No, no.",
    "start": 784.01,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "And now he lost some.",
    "start": 784.51,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Pull, Ty.",
    "start": 785.31,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler sees an opening.",
    "start": 785.81,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Using every aspect of his body,\nTyler's so close to glory.",
    "start": 787.14,
    "duration": 4.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Inside 5 yards.",
    "start": 791.24,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "[SCREAMS]",
    "start": 792.98,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Over the [INAUDIBLE].",
    "start": 793.78,
    "duration": 0.995
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody, fight him!",
    "start": 794.775,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody.",
    "start": 796.4,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Is one big pull enough here?",
    "start": 797.57,
    "duration": 2.85
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh!",
    "start": 800.42,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Could it be?",
    "start": 801.29,
    "duration": 0.7
  },
  {
    "text": "So close.",
    "start": 801.99,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Could it be?",
    "start": 802.49,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 803.79,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Got it!",
    "start": 804.29,
    "duration": 0.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Toney!",
    "start": 804.65,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Tyler Toney in an epic battle.",
    "start": 805.15,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL DINGS]",
    "start": 807.92,
    "duration": 0.54
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, first off, I just\nwant to say thanks to Cody.",
    "start": 808.46,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "He was a great competitor.",
    "start": 810.23,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't really mean that, but\nI feel like it's a formality.",
    "start": 811.35,
    "duration": 2.458
  },
  {
    "text": "I have to say it\nafter a competition.",
    "start": 813.808,
    "duration": 1.762
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyways, I vote we do\nanother one of these.",
    "start": 815.57,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "So I'm going to leave\nthe suit on until then.",
    "start": 817.65,
    "duration": 2.06
  },
  {
    "text": "Signing off for now.",
    "start": 819.71,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Pound it.",
    "start": 820.94,
    "duration": 0.69
  },
  {
    "text": "Noggin.",
    "start": 821.63,
    "duration": 0.51
  },
  {
    "text": "See you guys.",
    "start": 822.14,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Hope you have a great one.",
    "start": 823.01,
    "duration": 0.75
  },
  {
    "text": "[TEST TONE]",
    "start": 823.76,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "By the way, this isn't real.",
    "start": 824.26,
    "duration": 2.15
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, I'm still\nchubby under here.",
    "start": 826.41,
    "duration": 1.55
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHS] It's great.",
    "start": 827.96,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Pah.",
    "start": 829.67,
    "duration": 1.55
  }
]